Format AE listing analysis

Source: R/format_ae_listing.R
format_ae_listing.Rd

Format AE listing analysis

Usage

format_ae_listing(outdata, display_subline = FALSE)

Arguments

outdata

a outdata object created by prepare_ae_specific

display_subline

whether display subline or not.

Examples

library(metalite)
library(metalite.ae)
meta <- meta_ae_dummy()

lapply(prepare_ae_specific(meta, "apat", "wk12", "rel") |> 
collect_ae_listing() |>
format_ae_listing(), head, 100)
